-- Thomas Cook Puts Insurance Unit Up for Sale, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   J o h n   G l o v e r
-- 2012-07-22T07:55:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/thomas-cook-puts-insurance-unit-up-for-sale-sunday-times-says.html
Thomas Cook Group Plc (TCG)  has put its
White Horse Insurance unit up for sale seeking to raise as much
as 100 million pounds ($156 million), the  Sunday Times  reported,
without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
